    "en": {
      "title": "R.M.V. No work two days a week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Due to the current fuel crisis in the country, the Department of Motor Traffic has decided to close it until further notice on Thursday and Friday, Commissioner General of Motor Traffic Sumith Alahakoon said.",
        "The Werahera Driving License Office, Gampaha and Anuradhapura District Offices will be open on Thursdays only for clients booked online for Renewal of Driving Licenses. Says the Department of Motor Traffic.",
        "Services of the Department of Motor Traffic can be obtained by calling 0707677877 (Vehicle Registration and Transfer) and 0707677977 (Driving License) on office working days from 9.00 am to 4.00 pm and inquiring via Whatsapp / Viber / SMS messages after office hours. The department says."
      ],
